               <p>I live in Camomile-street; I have known him ten or twelve years; he has had very nigh 2000 l. of my property; he has an honest character in every respect.</p>
               <p>- CLARIDGE sworn.</p>
               <p>I have known him nine years; his character is undeniable; I trusted him with 1300 l. for very nigh six months; when I wanted money, there it was to a farthing.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17920215-30-person398">
