                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I live in Whitechapel; I have known him twenty-six years last October; he has the best of characters; he has had several hundreds of pounds pass through his hands.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17920215-30-person399">
                  THOMAS
                   ALLUM
               <interp inst="t17920215-30-person399" type="surname" value="ALLUM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17920215-30-person399" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17920215-30-person399" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I live in Chiswell-street; I have known him fifteen years; he kept my books ten years; he has an excellent character; I have trusted him with many hundreds.</p>
               <p>
            
